# 🍕 Pizza Sales Dashboard

An Excel dashboard created to analyze the performance of a fictional pizza restaurant.

## 📌 Dashboard Insights
- Total revenue, total orders, and average order value
- Best and worst selling pizzas
- Sales breakdown by category, size, and date
- Interactive slicers and visuals

## 📊 Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- PivotTables & PivotCharts
- Formulas & calculated fields
- Slicers and Timeline filters

## 📁 File
- `PIZZA_sales DASHBOARD.xlsx` – includes all visualizations and calculations

## 💼 Use Case
Ideal for showcasing Excel-based business intelligence and dashboarding skills.
